The Mild Basil Fried Rice with Fried Tofu was to die for!!! I'm a bit of a picky vegetarian eater, but I've been looking for good Thai restaurants for sixteen years and this is by far my favorite. Everything was delicious, the place was very clean, and the service was fast and friendly. Staff were very polite, and the atmosphere was very nice.

