Very good authentic Latin cuisine! Normally, it's quite difficult to find good Latin American food anywhere, especially if you're a vegetarian in Fountain Hills! Sofritas is quickly becoming my favorite proximity based restaurant, I've always been a big supporter of local businesses, and this place is definitely in my top five places to dine in FH. Staff are always very accommodating, the Guacamole and Hummus dishes are DELICIOUS! Food comes out very quickly as well, and the beautiful rustic crosses on the wall add to a wonderful Latin atmosphere. The place is beautifully kept and always very clean, 10/10, would definitely recommend!

