Penne alla Vodka was very filling and delicious! The sauce was excellently prepared, and the noodles were just the right texture. The bruschetta was made with some fairly fresh tomatoes, but the bread tasted smokey, possibly slightly burnt. Just okay. Garlic knots were great flavor for a good price. Will definitely be coming back!

